{"tid":1481694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"愛國愛港嘅黃絲全部入黎","createTime":"2019-08-17T20:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T05:15:39.000Z","uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cd90ef24652602bf982c0dd22214748aa18f1213","tid":1481694,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T20:21:49.000Z","msg":"共產黨既維穩方法，黎黎去去都係果幾招<br />\n對國內既文宣都係將香港既<span style=\"color: orange;\">內部政治矛盾，扭曲成 分離主義嘅外部勢力矛盾。</span><br />\n同時間 警察唔方便出面做既就用黑社會同&lsquo;愛國&rsquo;人士做醜人，然後用<span style=\"color: red;\">群眾鬥群眾做包裝</span>。<br />\n<br />\n解拆方法 就係 打著紅旗反紅旗<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同共產黨爭奪 「愛國」話語權。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n首先而家我地的確唔係搞緊獨立，反送中運動即使係革命，都係<span style=\"color: orange;\">保衛一國兩制，係制度上既革命</span>。所以<span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求本質上同愛國係可以並存，</span>而且可以<span style=\"color: orange;\">將反送中同守護一國兩制綑綁</span>。只係而家香港人對國家身分認同感低，所以唔會有人講愛國。但而家反送中片地開花，各行各業，連銀髮族都出黎 反送中，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解唔可以有愛國人士反送中呢？</span></span>我地要<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">再托闊我地既</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">想像力</span></span></span></span>！</span><br />\n<br />\n實際行動其實好簡單，只要用咗愛國既符號，做翻平時返送中做既野。例如<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">攞住中國國旗 ，著哂紅色衫</span> , <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">照舊示威, 照提出五大訴求, 甚至 光復香港，時代革命 都可以照嗌</span></span></span><br />\n好處係一個<span style=\"color: orange;\">擾敵之法</span>，攞咗國旗之後 差佬唔敢打你 黑社會或者大陸人都唔知你係唔係 打咗你又驚畀人影到相, 第二 當進行抗爭 ,任何人鬧你哋嘅時候, 都可以問佢哋愛唔愛國 佢話愛國嘅話, 就話而家我哋<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">維護緊鄧小平提出既一個兩制</span></span>. 甚至文宣都可以<span style=\"color: orange;\">搬鄧小平出黎</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">打住 保衛一國兩制 既旗號反送中。</span><br />\n<br />\n雖然大陸既民意無論支唔支持香港人反送中，對香港既抗爭無直接分別，因為<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">共產黨會高壓打擊香港係必然既</span></span>。但既然<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">共產黨先係香港既最大敵人，分化大陸人對香港人必然有利。</span></span><span style=\"color: orange;\">打著愛國旗幟向大陸反輸出革命</span>。而家習維尼行緊改革開放回頭路，搞到內憂外患，我地何不搬翻鄧小平呢個改革開放總設計師出黎，幫大陸人溫故知新，刺激一吓思考？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">愛國愛港</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">保衛一國兩制，<br />\n堅持五大訴求！</span></span>"},{"pid":"dd4ee3c5473397f74a61ff1590ba58885b685127","tid":1481694,"uid":300549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T20:59:41.000Z","msg":"我都覺得輸出革命係好重要，但又唔知應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d49f93237d8ecb0bf62e6ae954c8b19ff7443b10","tid":1481694,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T21:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/USKeXMs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUSKeXMs.png&h=f878df92&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd0a93c8dff1391ddaa34784cb5708c1e8b506eb","tid":1481694,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd4ee3c5473397f74a61ff1590ba58885b685127","tid":1481694,"uid":300549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T20:59:41.000Z","msg":"我都覺得輸出革命係好重要，但又唔知應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T21:23:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dt4bfCm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdt4bfCm.jpg&h=d51d7ee5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8dc02e7775e2fc5644e63fcb19fbef637fe21e20","tid":1481694,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T21:34:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"049f014f719815dca55e128947e6d08bab018e66","tid":1481694,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T21:34:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"27cb839edcfdb93eab90b3f206690a35a613164b","tid":1481694,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T21:34:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dc3b7a8b846be21fbd627b084f8785a77178b8f3","tid":1481694,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:59:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0d13813f971920fa940bf9d9755a20d806f08f7c","tid":1481694,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:15:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7KEGIyKlDzs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7KEGIyKlDzs&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1A1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=7b343b3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7KEGIyKlDzs</a>"},{"pid":"652fafbe5cce0386670cdb1e0fe4637d6acf60ce","tid":1481694,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T06:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AoLmFNv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAoLmFNv.jpg&h=e169bb1f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7055cbd4c9c371dab6ad6bd7de7b0721297eb5d","tid":1481694,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T06:13:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wwTjssC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwwTjssC.jpg&h=e3df7ccb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a09fe692c6698570bd2bfb99713df3fe9cf4d8b","tid":1481694,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sw2TDsJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsw2TDsJ.jpg&h=d260d848&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e57e0493f59dfd2d06f712f16fee93f022c85d4","tid":1481694,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:41:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkjam.com/?p=14147\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkjam.com%2F%3Fp%3D14147&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1A1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=aeffa9bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkjam.com/?p=14147</a><br />\n大陸格鬥狂人徐曉冬撐港年輕人，諷《環時》後遭公安「請喝茶」<br />\n<br />\n曾經踢爆中國武術界造假風氣的「格鬥狂人」徐曉冬，日前大膽在網路發表「撐香港年輕人」的言論，更暗諷《環球時報》失禮於世人前，最終卻遭公安「請喝茶」，幸暫時仍安全無恙。<br />\n<br />\n徐曉冬在直播中表示，他不希望、也不相信香港有那麼多「暴徒」，直言「很多暴徒都是假的」。徐曉冬表示，香港那些年輕人都是有為的年輕人，而有好多「暴徒」甚至不是香港人。徐曉冬表示，「某人被打了，我支持什麼什麼，你們打我吧&hellip;&hellip;最後身分發出來了吧，真他X丟人！」，此段發言疑是暗指《環球時報》記者付國豪遭人起底疑是國安單位的「臥底」。<br />\n<br />\n徐曉冬又針對公開撐警察的中國藝人，指很多中國藝人，其實都是香港籍，直指那些人是「愛國賊」。徐曉冬表示，「自己查查，有多少（藝人）都是香港籍的？你們罵半天香港人，你們自己都是。」；「很多明星影星，你敢站出來曬曬你的國籍嗎？好意思嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n然後他霸氣強調：「我的朋友圈，誰在試圖分裂國家，抹黑香港同胞，惡意誇大各別事件的各別壞份子，滾出我的朋友圈！自己解決，千萬不要被邪惡勢力蒙騙！造成香港同胞和大陸人民的互相敵意對立！」最後，徐曉冬表示，「記住別在我面前說港澳台同胞的壞話！小心大嘴巴煽你！」<br />\n<br />\n可是徐曉冬的激烈言論，最終卻換來被公安「約喝茶」的結果。其原定直播的時間，據網友指因為徐還在公安局而取消。後來徐曉冬在網上報平安，指自己還活著。"},{"pid":"443c13b72daea182b28e36d9244921f65075fe43","tid":1481694,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T18:22:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/reporter-08152019092544.html?encoding=traditional\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Freporter-08152019092544.html%3Fencoding%3Dtraditional&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1A1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=e1367f57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/reporter-08152019092544.html?encoding=traditional</a><br />\n《環時》記者香港機場遇襲　官方初高調譴責後降溫"},{"pid":"20b62abafa81125119129f3c5795bc1bb33ac080","tid":1481694,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T21:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jmaKfkW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjmaKfkW.jpg&h=59397417&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"454900d13b4b3d921057ca818aed78c19a462129","tid":1481694,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T22:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LvuGhEm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLvuGhEm.jpg&h=7aa23c73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b19c8b0b558d6ced69cdeb9b0c5aaaa43d47273","tid":1481694,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T11:34:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100010153272483/posts/955644038117363?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100010153272483%2Fposts%2F955644038117363%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1A1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=023fcc09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100010153272483/posts/955644038117363?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"2ab048c11dcf900fa17c8c145f93c522a2e7cbc8","tid":1481694,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T11:35:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/38Wa3s8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F38Wa3s8.jpg&h=1a089f6d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/23dgY1u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F23dgY1u.jpg&h=6ff5870b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4K4oD1u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4K4oD1u.jpg&h=2328d245&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NmBm98a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNmBm98a.jpg&h=cc1535c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xvU0GeQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxvU0GeQ.jpg&h=e935f798&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qa57meR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqa57meR.jpg&h=598e452b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XsG6BOb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXsG6BOb.jpg&h=cb5c1294&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fof3D1x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffof3D1x.jpg&h=af6b62b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/seqOP8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FseqOP8d.jpg&h=526f217a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/exRm98d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FexRm98d.jpg&h=a39980a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d94c2294730e1437c65f933a1875c18338e7e89","tid":1481694,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:12:13.000Z","msg":"深圳居民表示聽到十點大叫<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1513321\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1513321</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ee1a822f8a342b18ca471c5325d4355aff221047","tid":1481694,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:15:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/259780650868735/posts/1294809317365858?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F259780650868735%2Fposts%2F1294809317365858%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1A1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=209fcf60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/259780650868735/posts/1294809317365858?sfns=mo</a>"}]}